# Keep GitHub source archives (archive/*.tar.gz, "Download ZIP") runtime-only.
# Copy-based installs (Claude Code, Codex, OpenClaw, Grok CLI) fetch these
# archives, so dev/dist-only trees would otherwise ship inside every install —
# including skills/, the generated Hermes-only package (see README "Install").
# Hermes installs are unaffected: `hermes skills install` fetches through the
# GitHub Trees/Contents API, which ignores export-ignore.
/skills     export-ignore
/benchmarks export-ignore
/assets     export-ignore
/docs       export-ignore
/.github    export-ignore
